Easy Potato Soup

40 min
$6.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodEasy

Description

Creamy and comforting potato soup that's perfect for a cozy meal.

Ingredients

  • potatoes: 4 large, peeled and diced
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • milk: 1 cup
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • chives: for garnish
